title: Dungeon Twilight # 1-2
description:
Lewis Trondheim & Joann Sfar

Two books, 96 pages each
Published by NBM

An age of downfall: a final quest. The planet Terra Amata - on which Dungeon resides - has stopped turning. On one side, total darkness and absolute coldness: on the other, a searing desert, and eternal day. The survivors live on a thin slice of Terra where day and night meet. Twilight - welcome to the third facet of the Dungeon world: its dark downfall. Marvin, now old and blind and sensing his end, embarks on a final journey: the long, long trek to the legendary cemetery of the dragons.
